title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 - Jun 3 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 - Jun 3 2022
description:
Tim Kennedy, Green Beret sniper, UFC headliner, and author of the book "Scars and Stripes," joins Clay and Buck to talk Ukraine, Uvalde and the state of the U.S. military. Could Dr. Birx really be worse than Dr. Fauci? The worst possible argument: that we need more Joe Biden. C&B read 5-star podcast reviews.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
